reviews.review_text: This is actually a good Playin' In The Band.  The Swing Auditorium Playin' from last year 1977 was also fantastic, one of my favorites.
Close Encounters Tuning At the very end of Phil breaks a string - Bobby's Hunter joke Jerry rips out a quick riff in the last few second before Dire Wolf!
gave his all Jerry sings until there is nothing left.  What an effort!
well worth a listen because of the extra effort.  Recording is perfect.

Big Truckin at the Swing! *after promised land* 
Bob: “late again as usual” >
Hunter joke while Phil fixes a string 

22 minute Playin 

3 peak cycles on the end of Truckin, afterwards somebody says into the mic “pretty fuckin neat huh”
